        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Stop Onerous Surcharges Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires U.S. representatives to the International Monetary Fund (IMF) to advocate and vote for an immediate review of the IMF's surcharge policies and a suspension of such surcharges while the review is underway. <br> </p>]]>
        </text>
